LEVEL 1
  - first vote up
  - first vote down
  - first post
  - first answer
  - Conservator flag

LEVEL 2
  - Hero (50 vote up)
  - Minion (66 vote down)
  - Balancer (25 vote down && 25 vote up)
  - Censor (25 flags)
  - Prince (100 favorites for one question)
  - Follower (50 own favorites)
  - Conselour (100 answers)
  - phylosopher (100 questions)
  - Advocate (all badges level 1 , 4 level 2)
  
LEVEL 3
  - Angel (777 vote up)
  - Demon (666 vote down)
  - Famous (Question with more than 10000 views)
  - Verduge (150 flags)
  - King (100 favorites for one question)
  - Polyglot (Added more than 100 tags)
  - Oracle (100 right answers)
  - Maven Fan (Advocate Badge, 4 level 3)
